# RE Value - Real Estate Analytics

> Real estate data input, analytics dashboard, and reporting platform.

## Stack

| Layer | Technology |
|-------|-----------|
| Framework | Next.js 16 (App Router) |
| Styling | Tailwind CSS v4 |
| Language | TypeScript |
| Fonts | Inter (body), JetBrains Mono (terminal) |
| Design | Dark mode, data/terminal aesthetic, green/blue accents |

